ComicInfo.Summary: No one steals from Hyena without paying in blood! Barely surviving a demonic army's assault, Hyena and Quinn track their wretched enemies to their lair, determined to exact revenge on their elusive master. But nothing can prepare our heroes for this new hunting ground: a formal dinner party, attended by the vilest creatures in existence!
